Import reproducibility score notes

Source: R/import_notes.R
import_notes.Rd

Imports, formats data into proper types and calculates the final reproducibility score. Also adds the 2 and 5 year impact factor values from InCites Journal Citation Reports for 2018.

import_notes()

Value

A `tibble` object of reproducibility score notes formatted for use in analysis and manuscript preparation

Examples

notes <- import_notes()
pander::pander(head(notes))
